Constant Field Values
Constructor Detail

NumberedNameGenerator

public NumberedNameGenerator(java.lang.String prefix,
                             java.lang.String postfix)
Construct for names like [prefix].xxx.[postfix] with the default number of digits (=5).

Note that unless the prefix ends in a non-letter/digit character then a '.' will be postpended and that unless the postfix begins with a non-letter/digit character then a '.' will be prepended.

Parameters:
prefix - The prefix.
postfix - The postfix.

NumberedNameGenerator

public NumberedNameGenerator(java.lang.String prefix,
                             java.lang.String postfix,
                             int numDigits)
Construct for names like [prefix].xxx.[postfix].

Note that unless the prefix ends in a non-letter/digit character then a '.' will be postpended and that unless the postfix begins with a non-letter/digit character then a '.' will be prepended.

Parameters:
prefix - The prefix.
postfix - The postfix.
numDigits - The number of digits for the counter.
